title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 17 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 17 2022
description:
A tribute to Rush featuring Bo Snerdley, David Limbaugh, Mark Steyn and Todd Herman. The Canadian government begins to freeze the assets of donors to the trucker convoy. Rush on Biden's cognitive impairment. The latest on the Ukraine crisis. Canadian AG equivalent says Trump supporters should be worried about their bank accounts. Big Tech doxxing donors to Canadian truckers based on hacked info, same excuse they used for not reporting Hunter Biden story. C&B talk to a life-long Rush fan.
